OL,3,CAlan Carr buys 17-bedroom castle in
OL,4,Cthe Scottish Borders for #3.5 million
OL,6,FAlan Carr has bought a 17-bedroom
OL,7,Fcastle in the Scottish Borders for
OL,8,F#3.5 million.
OL,10,FThe comedian and TV host won the
OL,11,Fcelebrity version of The Traitors in
OL,12,F2025 which was filmed in the Scottish
OL,13,FHighlands.
OL,15,FHe has now purchased Ayton Castle near
OL,16,Fto the border between Scotland and
OL,17,FEngland and just a few miles from the
OL,18,Fcoast at Eyemouth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/2
