OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1772193711
OL,3,CAlan Carr buys 17-bedroom castle in
OL,4,Cthe Scottish Borders for #3.5 million
OL,6,FHis new title will be the Laird of
OL,7,FAyton as he signs a deal with Disney+
OL,8,Fto document the transformation of the
OL,9,Fproperty as he completes renovations.
OL,11,FThe castle dates mostly from the 19th
OL,12,Fcentury and had been in the hands of
OL,13,Fits previous owners since 2014.
